          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Images can contain metadata that reveals the orientation at capture time.  You can load this metadata into ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreimage/ciimage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreimage/ciimage/1547027-imagewithcontentsofurl",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreimage/ciimage/1437925-init",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " when the captured image contains orientation metadata.  Use any of the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "initWith:options: ",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "methods if the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreimage/ciimageoption/1437679-properties",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsdictionary",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " of metadata properties) option is also provided.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If the value of this key is true, then calls to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreimage/ciimage/1546997-imagewithcontentsofurl",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreimage/ciimage/1547016-imagewithdata",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " will return the image transformed according to its orientation metadata.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
